# Docs
*.md

# Raw GRF sprite dumps (여/남 subfolders, ~161MB) — runtime uses the flat
# resources/classes/<slug>.spr|.act only. This globs out every subdirectory
# under classes while keeping the flat slug files.
resources/classes/*/
